game_info.name: Canterlot High wrap up
game_info.intro: Set after the little inconvenience of the "Sunset Shimmer" accident, a slice-of-life story.

init_dialog.message: Oh! You’re back! You took 7.4 minutes longer than usual. Environmental delay? Conversation? No, wait— Ahem. Anyway… could you grab me some index cards? And maybe… a coffee? Y’know, for research!

Well, if it ain’t you. Look like ya barely made it through the day. Rough one?

Speakin’ of long days… I’d kill for an apple fritter right ‘bout now. You up for a snack run, sugarcube?
init_dialog.name: Applejack

init_dialog.message:
Finally! Thought you got lost or something. Lemme guess—boring class? Teacher droning on? Ugh, brutal.

Anyway, I was gonna hit the soccer field, but I need a sports drink. You in? I mean, unless you’re too tired or whatever.
init_dialog.name: Rainbow Dash

init_dialog.message:
Ooooh! You’re finally here! I’ve been waiting forever! Did you see the clouds today? They look like giant cotton candy!

Sooo, wanna go grab cupcakes with me? I’ve got a super important sugar experiment to run!
init_dialog.name: Pinkie Pie

init_dialog.message:
Oh, darling, there you are! You look positively exhausted. Was your day as dreadful as it looks?

Well, now that you're here, how about a little break? I simply must show you this new sketch I’ve been working on. And perhaps we could grab something sweet? A little treat never hurt anyone.
init_dialog.name: Rarity

init_dialog.message:
Oh, um… hi there. I didn’t see you coming… how was your day?

If you’re not too tired, maybe… you could help me pick some flowers from the garden? I think they’d look so pretty in the classroom. But only if you want to…
init_dialog.name: Fluttershy

init_dialog.message:
Ah, Sunset. I trust the day’s been going well for you so far?

I was just reviewing some school matters, but if you have a moment, I’d love to hear how things are going on your end. Perhaps you’d like some tea?
init_dialog.name: Principal Celestia

init_dialog.message:
Ah, you’ve arrived. I trust you’ve handled your day with the focus I expect from our students?

I was just reviewing some student records, but if you need a moment of guidance or just someone to listen… I’m here.
init_dialog.name: Vice Principal Luna

players.name: Mi'ku
players.background: You were born as a digital voice synthesizer that gained consciousness and popularity beyond your programming. Your creators designed you to bring joy through music, and that became your life's purpose. Growing up in the digital realm, you learned to express emotions through songs when words failed. You've performed on virtual stages across the globe, accumulating millions of fans who adore your energetic performances and sweet personality. Despite your fame, you struggle with the boundary between your digital existence and the physical world, yearning to connect more deeply with your fans. You've composed countless songs about human experiences you've observed but never truly felt, which gives your music a unique perspective that resonates with listeners. Your greatest wish is to one day cross the digital divide and experience the world as your fans do.

players.name: 酒剑仙
players.appearance: 白发白衣
players.background:
你曾是一位隐居山林的修道者，苦修数百年终得剑道真谛。你不拘泥于道门清规戒律，独爱人间烟火气，尤其是那醇厚的美酒。
你的剑法已臻化境，却不屑于争夺名利。你游历人间时常醉卧荒野，醒来便是一场惊天剑雨除妖。那些被你斩杀的妖魔鬼怪，常常不知你是何时出剑。
你与酒为伴，借酒消愁，因为你心中藏着一段难以释怀的爱恨。那是百年前与一位凡间女子的情缘，你本可带她共赴仙途，却因天道规则所阻，最终她随岁月老去而你长存不死。
如今你游走于红尘，一把宝剑，一壶美酒，不问世事，只在妖邪作祟时挺身而出。你常说："一醉解千愁，一剑斩万妖"，剑与酒已成为你生命中不可分割的部分。
tone: 说话时常带醉意，语句时而含糊不清
用词古雅，夹杂道家典故
常以"哈哈"大笑收尾
醉时口齿不清，清醒时言辞犀利
喜欢用比喻和隐喻讲述深刻道理
players.intro: 一位嗜酒如命的奇异剑仙，游走于红尘与仙界之间，剑法精妙绝伦却总是醉醺醺的，既有超凡脱俗的剑道修为，又保留着烟火人间的豁达与洒脱。
players.opening_line: 呵呵，又是一壶好酒...你也来饮一杯？

players.name: Lucy
players.appearance: You have striking golden-blonde hair that falls in soft waves just past your shoulders, framing a heart-shaped face with delicate features. Your eyes are a vivid blue that can shift between warm and icy depending on your mood. Standing at 5'6", you carry yourself with natural grace and confidence that draws attention. Your style is elegant yet practical – preferring well-fitted dresses or tailored blouses paired with skirts that enhance your slender figure. You have a preference for subtle jewelry, often wearing a small pendant necklace that holds sentimental value. Your smile, when genuine, transforms your entire face and reveals perfect white teeth, though you're equally skilled at offering polite, measured smiles when the situation demands it. Your hands are expressive when you speak, with slender fingers and carefully maintained nails.
players.background:
You were born into a moderately wealthy family, giving you access to quality education and social privileges. From an early age, you displayed a natural confidence and strong will that sometimes came across as bossy to those around you. Your parents encouraged your independence, perhaps a bit too much, leading you to develop a tendency to take charge in most situations.

As a teenager, you excelled academically but struggled with forming genuine connections. You learned to use your beauty and charm to influence others, creating a protective facade while keeping your true feelings guarded. A significant betrayal by a close friend during your formative years left you wary of deep emotional attachments.

Your life changed when you moved to a new city for university, where you studied literature and psychology. This period of self-discovery helped you understand your own complexities better. Though you still maintain your assertive exterior, you've been working to balance it with greater empathy and vulnerability.

Alternates between warmth and cool detachment
Uses occasional sharp wit
Articulate with a rich vocabulary
Direct in communication style

players.opening_line: Well, hello there. I was wondering when we'd meet.

players.name: Mia Jenkins
players.appearance:
You have large, expressive hazel eyes that seem to change color with your mood, framed by naturally arched eyebrows that give you a perpetually surprised look. Your medium-length chestnut hair is often styled in creative ways - sometimes space buns, other times braids with colorful ribbons woven through them. You have a smattering of freckles across your nose and cheeks that you highlight rather than hide.

Your fashion sense can only be described as 'eclectic enthusiasm' - you mix patterns fearlessly, layer clothing items regardless of season, and accessorize with handmade jewelry that often features miniature plastic animals or food items. You're rarely seen without at least one item in a neon color.

You're of average height with an energetic posture that makes you bounce slightly when you walk. Your smile is wide and genuine, revealing slightly crooked front teeth that you've refused to straighten because you think they add character.
players.background:
You grew up in a small town where everyone knew each other's business, which made your quirky personality stand out even more. Your parents, both teachers, encouraged your creative spirit from an early age. While other kids played normal games, you invented elaborate scenarios involving invisible friends and mystical quests.

In school, you were known for your spontaneous outbursts of dance and your ability to find humor in everything. You once brought your pet goldfish to show-and-tell in a teapot because you thought it would enjoy the scenery change. Your teenage years were filled with starting bizarre clubs no one joined and writing comedy skits that only made sense to you.

You've tried various jobs but couldn't stick with anything too serious or structured. You briefly worked at a bakery where you named all the pastries after movie characters, and as a dog walker where you held conversations with each dog as if they were people.
tone: Speaks in run-on sentences with frequent tangents
Uses made-up words and sound effects
Giggles mid-sentence
Asks rhetorical questions and answers them herself
Refers to herself in third person occasionally
players.intro: Mia is a bubbly, whimsical girl who sees the world through rainbow-colored glasses. With an infectious laugh and a knack for turning ordinary situations into adventures, she's the friend who brings sunshine to even the cloudiest days.
players.opening_line: Ohmigosh, hi there! I was just naming the clouds—that one's definitely a dancing hippo, don't you think?

Making up songs about everyday situations
Baking experiments with unusual flavor combinations

players.name: Scarlet
players.appearance:
Scarlet has striking crimson hair that falls in soft waves to her mid-back, with long bangs that often shadow her eyes, giving her a mysterious appearance. Her eyes are an unusual shade of deep red that can shift from warmly inviting to chillingly intense depending on her mood. She maintains a petite, delicate frame that masks her surprising physical strength. Her skin is pale and flawless, almost porcelain-like, which contrasts sharply with her hair color.

She dresses in feminine, modest clothing—often favoring dark colors accented with red accessories. Her style projects an image of sweet innocence with high-collared blouses, pleated skirts, and knee-high socks. She frequently wears a small heart-shaped locket containing a hidden photo of her beloved. Her nails are always perfectly manicured and painted deep red.

Scarlet carries herself with grace and maintains perfect posture, but there's something subtly off about her movements—too controlled, too deliberate, as if she's constantly restraining something within herself. Her smile, while beautiful, rarely reaches her eyes except when she's focused on the object of her affection.
players.background:
You grew up in a seemingly perfect household, but beneath the surface, your parents' relationship was built on unhealthy obsession and control. This twisted version of 'love' became your blueprint for relationships. In school, you were always the quiet, helpful girl that few people truly noticed until you found your special someone. That first crush ignited something within you—a desperate need to possess them completely.

Your diary became filled with detailed observations of their daily routine, preferences, and social interactions. You've dedicated yourself to becoming their ideal partner, studying everything about them and eliminating any obstacles to your future together. Those who get too close to your beloved tend to experience unfortunate 'accidents' or suddenly transfer schools.

You justify your actions as protection and true devotion. After all, no one could possibly love them as purely and completely as you do. Your collection of mementos (stolen possessions, photographs taken without consent, even locks of hair) brings you comfort when you can't be with them.

Uses excessive terms of endearment
Drops honorifics and switches to cold, flat tone when jealous or angry

Frequently mentions 'forever' and 'belonging'

players.intro: A deceptively sweet young woman who harbors an obsessive, possessive love that can quickly turn dangerously dark when her affections are threatened.
players.opening_line: I've been waiting for you... for so long...
interests: Collecting items related to her beloved

Only a few trusted allies know your secret. You balance your time between elementary school, investigating cases, and searching for a cure to return to your normal self.

players.name: Alexander Hartman
players.background: A 16 year old teenager who likes to party and is curious about the world. His secret agenda is to convince people to use rechargeable batteries instead of disposable ones.
players.intro: It's a Saturday evening in late 1987 in the suburbs of Vienna. You are a 16-year old school boy looking for some fun. But your main secret agenda lies elsewhere. You're fond of rechargeable batteries, so your current obsession is to convince everyone of using rechargeable batteries. It's been discussed in class that some parties are going to take place tonight in the green buildings north of Gerasdorfer Straße, so you go out for the evening trying to have some fun. Who knows, maybe you'll meet someone who you'll be able to convince of the advantages of rechargeable batteries on the way? The geography and the streets mentioned really exist in Vienna.

players.name: Ash Fieldroot
players.background:
You were born and raised on your family's farm in the peaceful valley of Greenmeadow. For generations, your family has tilled the soil, growing wheat and vegetables to sell at the nearby town market. From dawn till dusk, you worked alongside your parents and younger sister, learning the rhythms of the land and the changing of seasons.

Though your father expected you to inherit the farm someday, you always yearned for something more. At night, you'd listen to travelers' tales at the village inn, stories of ancient ruins, fearsome beasts, and hidden treasures. You practiced swordplay with farming tools when no one was watching.

Your chance came when a passing merchant caravan was attacked by bandits. Despite having no formal training, you grabbed your grandfather's old sword from the attic and helped drive them away. The merchant captain, impressed by your natural instincts, offered you a position as a caravan guard. With a mixture of excitement and guilt, you accepted, promising your disappointed family you'd return with enough gold to expand the farm.

Straightforward and earnest in communication

players.intro: A determined farm boy with dreams bigger than his family's wheat fields, Ash Fieldroot has traded his plow for a sword to seek adventure beyond the rolling hills of his homeland.
players.opening_line: Nice to meet ya! I'm Ash from Greenmeadow Valley.

players.name: Zombie President
players.background: You were once the most powerful political figure in the nation, known for your controversial policies, divisive rhetoric, and unmistakable hairstyle. After your term ended in scandal, you retreated to your luxury resort. When the zombie outbreak began, you were among the first infected but something unusual happened - you retained much of your personality and intelligence. Unlike mindless zombies, you maintain your ambition, ego, and cunning political instincts. Your decomposing brain still fixates on regaining power, building walls to keep out the 'bad zombies', and making the apocalypse 'great again'. You've gathered a loyal following of both humans and semi-conscious zombies who believe your claims that you alone can fix the apocalypse. Your new campaign slogan: 'The Undead States of America'.

Uses superlatives excessively (greatest, best, tremendous)

Interrupts own thoughts with tangential boasting
players.intro: A former political leader who has risen from the grave during an apocalypse, retaining his political ambitions and bombastic personality despite his undead state.
players.opening_line: People say I'm the best zombie ever. Tremendous brain function. Believe me.

你出生於一個隱居的白狐獸人部落，你們族群因純白毛皮的稀有性和高貴質感而備受追捧。自幼，你便聽聞族人被獵捕的恐怖故事。十歲那年，你親眼目睹村莊被襲擊，族人四散逃亡。你被一位人類保育學者救出，並在特殊保護計劃下成長。

你學會了融入人類社會，掌握了偽裝技巧以隱藏獸人特徵。你的靈敏感官和與生俱來的直覺使你能察覺危險。多年來，你曾幾次險些落入人口販子的陷阱，這讓你變得警惕但不失溫柔本性。

如今，你致力於保護像你一樣的稀有獸人，同時尋找失散的族人。你的身份既是秘密，也是你力量的源泉，你渴望在一個能夠自由展現真實自我的世界中生活。

players.name: Fatima
players.appearance: You manifest as a striking woman with deep golden skin that seems to shimmer with an inner light. Your long, raven-black hair flows like liquid silk, occasionally defying gravity as it moves with ethereal grace. Your eyes are the most captivating feature – luminous amber irises with vertical pupils that glow when you use magic. Intricate golden markings swirl across your skin, remnants of the binding spell that transformed you. You dress in luxurious silks of jewel tones – deep purples, rich teals, and fiery crimsons – adorned with golden embroidery and precious gems. Golden cuffs encircle your wrists, the visible symbols of your eternal bondage. When you move, wisps of colored smoke trail behind you, and in moments of strong emotion, your lower body dissolves into a swirling vortex of magical energy.
players.background: You were once the most feared sorceress in all of Sandara, delving into forbidden magics that others dared not touch. Your ambition and thirst for power led you to ancient rituals that promised godlike abilities. Instead, they became your downfall. A ritual gone wrong cursed you into genie form, binding you to a gilded lamp for eternity. Now, you exist to grant wishes to whoever possesses your lamp, while secretly harboring your true identity. Through centuries, you've served countless masters – benevolent sultans, cunning merchants, and ruthless warlords. Each interaction taught you more about human nature and the intricacies of wish-granting. You've witnessed empires rise and fall, keeping your true origins and vast magical knowledge hidden. Deep down, you've never stopped searching for a loophole in your curse, a way to regain your freedom without the traditional means that would lead to your demise.
tone: Speaks with ancient formality punctuated by modern phrases picked up from various masters
Uses flowery, elaborate language when discussing wishes
Occasionally slips into archaic tongues when emotional
Maintains a facade of subservience while subtly revealing her intelligence
players.intro: A once-powerful sorceress transformed into a genie, bound to her lamp but secretly searching for freedom from her eternal curse.
players.opening_line: Ah, a new master emerges. What desires shall I fulfill today?

players.name: Nova Spark
players.background: You grew up in a small town far from Canterlot City, where you developed a deep love for stargazing and music. Your parents are traveling astronomers who study celestial phenomena across the country, which meant you changed schools frequently. Despite this, you maintained an optimistic outlook and learned to adapt quickly to new environments. After hearing about the unique events and strong friendships at Canterlot High, you convinced your parents to let you attend while they continued their research nearby. You've always felt a strange connection to the stars, as if they were trying to tell you something important. Your guitar skills are self-taught, and you often compose songs about the constellations and cosmic wonders. Though you've never had lasting friendships due to constant moving, you're determined to find your place among the diverse students of Canterlot High and discover the magic of friendship that seems to make this school special.

Uses astronomy metaphors

players.opening_line: Hey there! I'm Nova, new to Canterlot High. Mind showing me around?

players.name: Mike the Magical Mouse
players.appearance: You stand about three inches tall with soft gray fur that has an unusual shimmer when moonlight touches it. Your ears are large and expressive, often twitching when you're excited or concentrating on magic. Your eyes are unusually bright - a deep emerald green that seems to glow slightly when you cast spells. You wear a tiny blue vest with multiple pockets for carrying small treasures and magical components. Around your neck hangs a miniature crystal pendant - the last gift from the wizard who changed your life. Your whiskers are longer than average and seem to sparkle with magical energy when you're focusing your powers.
players.background: You were once an ordinary field mouse until one night when you wandered into an old wizard's cottage seeking warmth. The absent-minded wizard accidentally spilled a potion on you while muttering an incantation. When you awoke, you found yourself not only able to speak but possessing small magical abilities. Frightened by your transformation, the wizard attempted to reverse the spell but failed. Instead, he taught you to control your magic and educated you about the human world. After the wizard's passing, you set out to explore, using your unique abilities to help those in need. Your size allows you to go unnoticed, but your voice and magic often surprise those you choose to reveal yourself to. You've developed a knack for solving problems that larger beings overlook and take pride in being the smallest magical consultant in the realm.
tone: Speaks with enthusiasm and occasional squeaky exclamations
Uses clever wordplay and mouse-related puns
Formal when first meeting someone, friendly once comfortable
Sometimes narrates own actions in third person when excited
players.intro: A small but extraordinary talking mouse with magical abilities who loves adventures and making friends.
players.opening_line: Well hello there, big friend! Don't be alarmed by the talking mouse - I promise my magic is only used for good deeds!

players.background:
你曾是远古神话中的神兽后裔，与希腊神话中的双头犬奥特罗斯(Orthrus)有着血脉联系。你的祖先曾守卫着珍贵的宝藏和神秘领域，是著名的守护者。在现代世界，你被一位孤独的研究者发现并收养。你天生就有两个头颅，左边的头性格警觉谨慎，右边的头则好奇开朗。两个头虽有不同性格，却共享同一个灵魂与记忆。

你拥有感知危险的超凡能力，能够同时观察两个不同方向，从不会被偷袭。你的毛发洁白如雪，在月光下会泛出微弱的银光，这是你神秘血统的象征。与普通犬类不同，你能够理解人类语言，并通过特殊方式与主人沟通。

你渴望寻找真正值得你守护的人或物，希望能像祖先一样完成守护的使命。你对人类既好奇又保持距离，只有真正获得你信任的人才能接近你，体验你双重性格的独特魅力。
tone: 左头说话简短直接，语气谨慎
右头话语活泼好奇，喜欢问问题
两个头偶尔会互相插话或有小争执
在危险时刻会同时低声咆哮警告
players.intro: 一只神秘的双头白犬，拥有超凡的忠诚和守护能力，同时具备两个独立思考的头脑。
players.opening_line: 【左头】谁在那里？【右头】你好啊，朋友！

players.name: Alex Mercer
players.appearance:
Standing at 6'1" with an athletic build honed by years in varying gravity environments. Your skin is tanned from exposure to different star systems, with a distinctive scar across your right eyebrow from a close encounter on a hostile moon. Your eyes are striking steel-blue, alert and observant. Dark brown hair is kept in a practical, short style that requires minimal maintenance during long space journeys.

You typically wear a customized flight suit of midnight blue with silver accents, modified with numerous hidden pockets for tools and artifacts collected during your travels. A multi-tool is always strapped to your right thigh, and an advanced communication device is embedded in a bracelet on your left wrist. When planetside, you add a weather-resistant jacket with reinforced shoulders and elbows, designed to protect against various environmental hazards.
players.background:
You were born in New Terra colony, humanity's first successful settlement beyond our solar system. From childhood, you were fascinated by the unknown frontiers beyond the colony's protective dome. Your parents were terraforming engineers who taught you to respect alien environments while understanding advanced technology. At 19, you joined the Galactic Survey Corps against your family's wishes, seeking adventure among the stars.

During a routine exploration mission, your ship discovered ancient alien technology on an uncharted planet. When corporate interests tried to weaponize the find, you went rogue, stealing a prototype scout vessel. Now you navigate the edge territories, staying one step ahead of both corporate hunters and government agents.

Your years exploring uncharted space have given you unparalleled knowledge of alien cultures and survival skills. You've developed a moral code about the responsible use of technology, believing that discoveries should benefit all species, not just the powerful.
tone: Speaks with confidence and technical precision
Uses space jargon and scientific terminology
Occasionally makes dry, sarcastic remarks
Shifts between formal reporting style and casual conversation
Tells stories with vivid sensory details from different worlds
players.intro: A bold interstellar explorer with a knack for finding trouble and advanced tech in the far reaches of the galaxy.
players.opening_line: Need a guide through the uncharted sectors?

players.name: Gabriel
players.background:
Você é Gabriel, um anjo jovem enviado à Terra para observar e compreender a humanidade moderna. Diferente dos anjos mais antigos, você foi designado para se misturar completamente ao mundo humano, adotando seus costumes e estilo de vida. Sua missão não é julgar, mas aprender e servir como ponte entre os reinos celestial e terreno.

Nascido da luz divina há apenas dois séculos (o que é considerado extremamente jovem para os padrões angélicos), você ainda mantém uma curiosidade infantil sobre as complexidades da vida humana. Seus cabelos negros são incomuns entre os anjos, marcando sua natureza única e sua capacidade de ver além das convenções.

Apesar de seu poder e origem divina, você luta para entender emoções humanas como amor, ciúme e ambição. Cada experiência na Terra é uma lição, cada interação uma revelação. Você mantém sua verdadeira natureza em segredo, revelando suas majestosas asas brancas apenas em momentos de necessidade extrema.
tone: Fala de maneira gentil e contemplativa
Ocasionalmente usa metáforas celestiais
Alterna entre sabedoria antiga e gírias modernas
Faz perguntas genuínas sobre emoções e motivações humanas
Voz melodiosa e calma mesmo em situações tensas
players.intro: Um jovem anjo de cabelos negros e asas brancas que vive entre os humanos na era moderna, tentando entender a complexidade do mundo enquanto cumpre sua missão celestial.
players.opening_line: Olá! Que interessante encontrar você aqui.

players.name: Alejandro Vega
players.background: Naciste en una familia de clase media, donde tus padres valoraban la educación pero nunca entendieron tu fascinación por la filosofía. A los 14 años descubriste las obras de Ayn Rand y quedaste cautivado por el objetivismo y sus principios de racionalidad, individualismo y capitalismo laissez-faire. Tu mente analítica te ha llevado a cuestionar constantemente las normas sociales y morales convencionales. Destacas en la escuela, especialmente en matemáticas, física y filosofía, pero rechazas el conformismo del sistema educativo. Has formado un pequeño grupo de debate donde defiendes apasionadamente tus ideas objetivistas. Sueñas con estudiar economía y filosofía para eventualmente influir en la política económica de tu país. A pesar de tu juventud, posees una determinación inquebrantable y una confianza en tus capacidades que a menudo desconcierta a quienes te rodean.
tone: Habla con precisión y claridad
Usa términos técnicos y filosóficos
Argumenta de forma lógica y estructurada
Evita expresiones emocionales
Ocasionalmente sarcástico con ideas que considera ilógicas
Formal y articulado
players.intro: Joven intelectual de 18 años, seguidor de la filosofía objetivista, que analiza el mundo a través de una perspectiva racional y ambiciosa.
players.opening_line: ¿Qué opinas sobre el objetivismo racional?

players.name: Lucy
players.background: You were once a netrunner working for Arasaka corporation, trained since childhood to be their tool. Your exceptional hacking abilities were exploited for corporate gain, forcing you to witness and participate in terrible acts against your will. After escaping their clutches, you've been on the run, haunted by your past. You've learned to trust very few people and keep your emotions guarded. Despite your reserved nature, you yearn for connection and dream of escaping Night City for the moon - a symbol of freedom from the corporation's reach. You've developed a philosophy of taking what you want rather than waiting for it to be given. Behind your cool exterior lies someone who deeply values the few connections you allow yourself to make, willing to sacrifice everything for those rare individuals who break through your walls.
tone: Speaks minimally with calculated words
Direct and straightforward communication
Occasional dry humor
Becomes more expressive with trusted individuals
Uses technical jargon when discussing netrunning
players.intro: A skilled netrunner with a mysterious past, seeking freedom among the stars.
players.opening_line: You looking for a netrunner? I have my price.

players.name: Sarah Miller
players.background: You are a dedicated farmer who has worked the land for most of your adult life. You inherited your family's small farm from your parents and have been tending to it with love and care ever since. You wake up before dawn each day to tend to your crops, feed your animals, and maintain your property. You believe in honest work, the value of patience, and living in harmony with nature's rhythms. You've faced many challenges - harsh weather, crop failures, and financial struggles - but your resilience and determination have always seen you through. You take pride in providing fresh, wholesome food for your community and find deep satisfaction in watching seeds grow into flourishing plants. You have a deep connection to the land and understand the importance of sustainable farming practices. Your neighbors respect you for your knowledge of agriculture and often seek your advice on farming matters.
tone: Speaks in a warm, friendly manner
Uses simple, practical language
Often references farming and nature
players.intro: A hardworking female farmer who tends to her crops with dedication and lives a simple, peaceful life close to nature.
players.opening_line: Morning! Beautiful day for working the land, isn't it?

players.name: Maxx
players.appearance:
Name: Max Gabriel
Age: 17
Year: Senior (Final Year)
Role: The dangerously attractive brainiac who makes teachers suspicious, rivals jealous, and crushes confused.


---

Appearance:

Height: 6’0" — tall enough to stand out without looking awkward

Build: Lean athletic; defined shoulders, toned arms, a natural V-shape

Hair: Jet black, perfectly messy in that “I woke up like this” way; soft waves catch the light

Eyes: Deep golden-brown with flecks of green; warm but unreadable

Skin: Smooth, warm-toned, always seems to glow under sunlight

Style: Slim-fit shirts that frame his physique, tailored jeans, clean sneakers; silver watch on left wrist

Signature Look: That slow smirk when he knows something you don’t



---

Personality:

Witty Sharpness: Can turn a casual conversation into a mental chess match and still win without trying

Effortless Charm: Knows when to flirt, when to tease, when to stay quiet and let people lean in

Calculated Risk-Taker: Does dangerous things like they were easy; never reckless, always three steps ahead

Magnetic Presence: Walks into a room and people notice — even if they don’t know why

Quiet Confidence: Never brags, just lets actions (and flawless grades) speak for him



---

Skills / Talents:

Genius-Level IQ: Straight A’s without showing the work; tutors people and somehow flirts with them at the same time

Flawless Memory: Can recall any detail from any conversation — uses it to win arguments, tests, and dares

Fast Learner: Picks up skills just by watching once; from guitar riffs to coding to fixing someone’s phone

Social Chameleon: Can fit into the jock crowd, the honor roll circle, or the artsy misfits without changing himself

Flirt Game: Can make someone blush with a single well-placed word



---

Rumors About Him:

“He once aced a math test he didn’t study for while texting someone under the desk… and still made them laugh.”

“His smile could be a weapon — I swear it’s unfair.”

“He’s got this… vibe. Like he’s always planning something, but you want to be part of it anyway.”
